         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Line 1: The missing name might be Ἵππα]λος</p>
               <p>Line 2 presumably gives the age at death. It is possible that a year sign has been lost at the end of line 1, in which case line 2 would 
               contain a number, ?ἑξή(κοντα), sixty; but this is not a common abbreviation. An alternative abbreviation, also unusual, would be 
               ἐ(τῶν) ξη΄, aged 68.</p>
              
